*Android Application Fundamentals (Activities, Services, Broadcasts, Content providers) : http://developer.android.com/guide/topics/fundamentals.html
*Android Dev - Intents : http://developer.android.com/guide/topics/intents/intents-filters.html
*Routing Intents : http://developer.android.com/resources/articles/wikinotes-intents.html
*Open Intents : http://www.openintents.org/en/
*Open Intents Applications : http://www.openintents.org/en/download
*Registry of Open Intents Protocol : http://www.openintents.org/en/intentstable
*Open Intent Libraries : http://www.openintents.org/en/libraries
*List of intents provided by Google : http://developer.android.com/guide/appendix/g-app-intents.html
*Hacking the wheelchair joystick onto the Android's trackball : http://groups.google.com/group/android-platform/browse_thread/thread/73eed70fb229d7ae?pli=1
*Eyes-Free Shell : http://code.google.com/p/eyes-free/
*GSoC TimeLine : http://socghop.appspot.com/document/show/gsoc_program/google/gsoc2010/faqs#timeline
